51:51.166 --> 51:53.875
Before that, Janis Joplin
with "Get It While You Can",

51:53.958 --> 51:56.416
and a song of the same name
by Robert Finley

51:56.500 --> 51:57.958
right before that on the show.

51:58.041 --> 51:59.708
Now, here's an obscure
little gem

51:59.792 --> 52:01.708
for all your audiophiles
out there.

52:01.792 --> 52:03.708
This is a Dixieland revival
romp,

52:03.792 --> 52:07.458
peaking at number two
on the Billboard Hot 100, 1963,

52:07.541 --> 52:09.625
and it's one
of my personal favorites.

52:09.708 --> 52:10.917
Here it is.

